<style>
  .form-head{
    display:flex;
    align-items:flex-start;
    justify-content:space-between;
    gap:12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .form-head h2{
    margin:0;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 650;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .form-head .sub{
    margin: 2px 0 0;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .form-actions{
    display:flex;
    gap:8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:flex-end;
  }

  .form-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .field{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:6px;
  }
  .field label{
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .input, .textarea{
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0 12px;
    height: 40px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
  }
  .textarea{
    height: auto;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    min-height: 110px;
    resize: vertical;
  }
  .input:focus, .textarea:focus{
    outline:none;
    border-color: var(--text);
    box-shadow: var(--ring);
  }

  .span-2{ grid-column: 1 / span 2; }

  .hint{
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .footer-actions{
    display:flex;
    gap:8px;
    justify-content:flex-end;
    margin-top: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px){
    .form-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .span-2{ grid-column: auto; }
  }
</style>

<div class="form-head">
  <div>
    <h2>신규 계약 등록</h2>
    <div class="sub">계약 기본정보를 입력하고 저장하세요</div>
  </div>

  <div class="form-actions">
    <a href="/contract" class="btn">목록</a>
  </div>
</div>

<form method="post" action="/contract/new" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <div class="form-grid">

    <div class="field">
      <label>계약번호</label>
      <input class="input" type="text" name="contract_no" placeholder="예: CT-2025-001" />
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label>발주처</label>
      <input class="input" type="text" name="client_name" placeholder="예: ○○건설 / ○○기관" />
    </div>

    <div class="field span-2">
      <label>계약명 <span style="color:#ef4444;">*</span></label>
      <input class="input" type="text" name="title" placeholder="계약명을 입력하세요" required />
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label>계약금액</label>
      <input class="input" type="number" name="total_amount" placeholder="숫자만 입력 (원)" min="0" step="1" />
      <div class="hint">표시는 저장 후 목록에서 자동으로 천 단위 구분됩니다.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label>등록일(표시용)</label>
      <input class="input" type="text" name="created_at" placeholder="자동 생성/혹은 비워두기" />
      <div class="hint">DB에서 자동 생성한다면 이 항목은 제거해도 됩니다.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label>공사 시작일</label>
      <input class="input" type="date" name="start_date" />
    </div>

    <div class="field">
      <label>공사 종료일</label>
      <input class="input" type="date" name="end_date" />
    </div>

    <div class="field span-2">
      <label>계약서 PDF 첨부</label>
      <input class="input" style="padding-top:7px;" type="file" name="pdf_file" accept="application/pdf" />
      <div class="hint">PDF 업로드 기능이 라우트/DB에 아직 없다면, 이 항목은 숨겨두고 나중에 연결해도 됩니다.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="field span-2">
      <label>비고</label>
      <textarea class="textarea" name="memo" placeholder="특이사항 / 첨부자료 메모"></textarea>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="footer-actions">
    <a href="/contract" class="btn">취소</a>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">저장</button>
  </div>
</form>
